cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper deals with program synthesis and program repair, which are both subfields of programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses reachability, which is a topic in logic and verification (cs.LO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper applies its approach to program repair to fix bugs, which falls under the category of computer security and cryptography (cs.CR).
